          <p>Large-scale industrial TPO membrane installation featuring advanced drainage and insulation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=600" alt="Roof Inspection">
        <div class="card-content">
